requires a tool that removes AACS protection. For example Passkey Lite or AnyDVD HD.</li> <li>Supports streaming video from Youtube, Twitch, and many other websites.<br /> Requires placing <a href="https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp" target="_blank">yt-dlp.exe</a> in MPC-HC folder.</li></ul><p>Other notable features:</p><ul><li>Fast thumbnail generation in Explorer for all your video files.</li> <li>Includes utility for configuring and managing the installed codecs.</li> <li>Frequent updates and smart support staff.</li></ul><h1><!-- google_ad_section_end --></h1><div id="GASkyCode" style="display: none;"><script type="text/javascript">google_ad_client="ca-pub-2002140396092627";google_ad_slot="2086603737";google_ad_width=160;google_ad_height=600;</script><script type="text/javascript" src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js"></script></div><script type="text/javascript">window.onload = function() {document.getElementById('GASky').appendChild(document.getElementById('GASkyCode'));document.getElementById('GASkyCode').style.display = '';}</script></td></tr><tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="footer"></td><td align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="footer">Copyright 2004-2023, Codec Guide. All rights reserved.<br /> Usage of this website implies acceptance of our <a href="termsofuse.htm" target="_self">Terms of Use</a> and <a href="privacypolicy.htm">Privacy Policy</a>.<br /> <a href="contact.htm" target="_self">Contact</a></td></tr></table></div><div class="rightcol"></div></div></body></html>